The paper discusses the problem of attack detection, which is a common topic in computer security (cs.CR). The approach taken in the paper is to model the interaction between the defender and attacker as a game, which is a common technique in game theory (cs.GT). The game involves the use of a classifier, which is a common tool in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of adaptive attacks, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
